This cover will forever go down in my personal history book as one of the fav projects of my career! The energy on set creating with the masterful @stylequon and crazy genius @audreytaylorvisuals was like fire .. totally flow state.. and just soooo dang fun. Beyond grateful for this moment to share our over the top interpretation of @justinchapple ‘s seafood tower recipes with the world! We hope it inspires you to go all out and throw down for the holidays… spoil the heck out of your nearest and dearest in whatever love language you are most fluent in! (Mine is good duh!) Thank you thank you to everyone at @foodandwine for entrusting us with concepting and photographing this years holiday cover! Total honor and dream come true. Thx also to @instacubs @surlyspice and @laurajeannapkins 💪🏼

Just a little tradition over here @studiokolenko ! After a beautiful shoot week I express my gratitude to my amazing team in liquid form. Cocktails are my love language! This week, I’m making a Naked and Famous (ish) that originated  @deathandcompany It’s a crowd pleaser, even if you have non-mezcal loving weirdos in your crew, everyone I have ever met loves this drink and asks me for the recipe. So here it is! It’s genius-ly simple to mix up. You can riff on it endlessly subbing the main booze for your fav and switch out the citrus to whatever you have on had… (I used lemons here, but the traditional recipe is with lime) And bonus ..you can batch it for parties… like #superbowllvii *TIP* !!! There is chartreuse shortage out there! ITS REAL! Sub in elderflower liquor if you can’t find chartreuse.  #equalpartscocktails #nakedandfamous #evabartendstheset #gratitude #ilovemycrew #mylovelanguage #studiokolenko #friday #friyay #fridaycocktails #illdrinktothat #happyhour

I got to send my rep of 19 years @sharpela ( @sharpeonline ) off into retirement with a surprise lunch yesterday. He had no idea I was in town! We caught up like close long time friends do .. but it’s hard… we’ll impossible really, to express everything this man has meant to me over the years in a few short hours. 19 years ago He pulled me into the fold amongst a roster of photographers like @zacharyscott_studio and @hugh_kretschmer whom I was completely starstruck by before I had even graduated from art school.. just a tiny tiny photographer baby and he has played a major role in the photographer I’ve become today. His integrity, honestly and huge heart makes him a rare breed .. and DANG we had so much freakin fun! Congratulations John on this huge moment .. I’m so excited to see you usher in this new season of your life and all the good you are going to do for this world and community with all your extra time. Love you!

My greenhouse baby veg starts graduate to the garden today.  Still waiting on basil, peppers and watermelon to grow up.. but otherwise the rest of the garden is in.. finally. I rarely get 1/2 a day to garden like I did today. A majority of this years garden came together in multiple 30 min to 1 hr chunks of time every week over the corse of 3 months. Consistently taking small steps still gets you to the goal! Here is proof. Food from the ground goals well on their way. #evaskitchengarden #passionproject #humanswhogrowfood #eatehatyougrow #mygarden #backyardgarden
